{"tid":2060133,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"詩人王藏涉「煽顛罪」遭警帶走 妻被扣押通宵後獲釋","createTime":"2020-06-11T11:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T11:52:18.000Z","uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25724440c2e20f34ae7136c03d72aea522bc4209","tid":2060133,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"國安法就係咁樣<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200601/Z5ODURJDVCAM6YAEPDMBXT25QI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200601%2FZ5ODURJDVCAM6YAEPDMBXT25QI%2F&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0pE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=20f927c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200601%2FZ5ODURJDVCAM6YAEPDMBXT25QI%2F&h=cf42f825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200601/Z5ODURJDVCAM6YAEPDMBXT25QI/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/0530Wlq/status/1270931403476090880?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0530Wlq%2Fstatus%2F1270931403476090880%3Fs%3D20&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0pE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=9757573d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F0530Wlq%2Fstatus%2F1270931403476090880%3Fs%3D20&h=e19b17fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/0530Wlq/status/1270931403476090880?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"34589040e3846e6848f2343dac6e4b908df7b173","tid":2060133,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"六四31周年倒數在即，內地異見人士、詩人王藏又遭警方控制。其妻王麗透露，5月30日下午，王藏被雲南省楚雄市公安局以「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」名義帶走。王麗本人也被警方帶走，家中重要文件，以及銀行卡、身份證、護照等也被一併拿走。<br />\n<br />\n王麗在公安局被扣押到31日，直至凌晨3時才回到家，至今仍被警方監控；而丈夫王藏目前身在何處，則不得而知。<br />\n消息傳出後，海內外維權人士都關注事件。身在國內的維權律師倪玉蘭和身在美國的律師陳建剛，都在Twitter上呼籲關注王藏的遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n王藏本名王玉文，是國際筆會獨立中文筆會會員，其詩作充滿現實關懷和批判性，曾在社交媒體公開支持香港佔中運動﹐早前曾轉載與歌手何韻詩的短片。多年來，王藏和家人屢遭中國政府打壓，2018年更被迫從北京遷回其家鄉雲南。"}]}